<div><head>《集靈記》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.2">王諿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.3">琅邪人也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.4">仕梁為南康王記室。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.5">亡後數年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.6">妻子困於衣食。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.7">歲暮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.8">諿見形謂婦曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.9">「卿困乏衣食？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.10">妻因與之酒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.11">別而去。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.12">諿曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.13">「我若得財物，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.14">當以相寄。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.15">後月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.16">小女探得金指環一雙。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1538_CHANT_001-1a.17">御覽七百十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
